2. WE are alſo to pray for every particular perſon, that ſhall ſtand in need of our prayers;
                        Some ſay that S. Stephens prayer procured S. Pauls converſion: Si Stephanus nòn oraſſet, Eccleſia Paulum è Saulo nòn habuiſſet. Aug.
                      Thus we are to pray for Papiſts, Hereticks, Schiſmaticks, that God would convert them; though we are not to pray with them, as perſons out of the Communion of Saints; yet are we to pray for them, being of our own fleſh: we know not how God hath decreed concerning them.

